title: Dakine Cobra Glove
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Cobra Glove in our Cobalt print.
Cobra Features:
- Insert: Gore Tex® Waterproof / Breathable
- Insulation: High loft synthetic [ 60 / 220g ]
- Palm: Durable water repellent leather
- Shell Fabric: Nylon / Poly with DWR treatment and durable water repellent leather
- Lining: 230g fleece / 400g Pile
- Cuff Closure: Zipper
- Nose wipe thumb panels
